reviews.text: Ocean Centre is a sprawling shopping centre that's located right on the harbour of Tsim Sha Tsui. There's a lot of variety in here but most of the goods are from the higher end brands and designers. They always have the latest and the shopping experience here is nice. There's also a good number of restaurants. The toilets here are very clean.
Quite some nice shops and restaurants with a small outdoor area at the very end and little later on the top deck.
Refused entry at 2pm!!! (Lunchtime hours listed as 1pm to 3pm) An absolute disgrace. Do they discriminate against Western customers?? Avoid this restaurant at all cost!!!
